---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Fleet Charging Solutions — Evium Charging"
  description="Turnkey EV fleet charging infrastructure. Depot design, load management, phased rollout, and 24/7 monitoring — engineered for fleets that can't afford downtime."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-[#0a1822]">

    <!-- Background atmosphere -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_70%_60%_at_65%_50%,rgba(45,200,86,0.10),transparent)]"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-evium-green/30 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Charger image -->
    <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-[52%] h-full pointer-events-none select-none flex items-end justify-end">
      <img
        src="/images/chargers/maxicharger/maxicharger-dc-fast-60-240kw.png"
        alt="MaxiCharger DC Fast Charger for Fleet Depots"
        class="h-[88%] object-contain object-bottom drop-shadow-[0_0_80px_rgba(45,200,86,0.20)]"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Diagonal dark overlay so left text stays readable -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="background: linear-gradient(100deg, #0a1822 50%, transparent 72%);"
    ></div>

    <!-- Left content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 pt-32 pb-24">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <p class="text-evium-green text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-5">Fleet Charging Infrastructure</p>
        <h1 class="text-white font-black leading-[1.06] mb-6" style="font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5.5vw, 5rem);">
          Every Vehicle.<br />
          Mission-Ready.<br />
          <span class="text-evium-green">Every Morning.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-md">
          Fleet electrification isn't a product — it's a strategy. Evium designs, deploys, and operates depot charging infrastructure built around your vehicles, your shifts, and your grid.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center">
          <a
            href="/contact/quote"
            class="inline-block bg-evium-green text-[#0a1822] font-black text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase px-8 py-4 hover:bg-white transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            Talk to a Fleet Specialist
          </a>
          <a
            href="#fleet-challenge"
            class="inline-block text-white/65 font-semibold text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-8 py-4 border border-white/20 hover:border-evium-green hover:text-evium-green transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            See What We Build
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats row -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-10 mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <div>
            <div class="text-evium-green font-black text-3xl">500+</div>
            <div class="text-white/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Chargers Deployed</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-evium-green font-black text-3xl">24/7</div>
            <div class="text-white/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Remote Monitoring</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-evium-green font-black text-3xl">$6MM+</div>
            <div class="text-white/40 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Grants Secured</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE FLEET ELECTRIFICATION CHALLENGE
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="fleet-challenge" class="bg-evium-dark py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">

      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
        <p class="text-evium-green text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-4">Why Most Fleet Programs Stall</p>
        <h2 class="text-white font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-6">
          You Can't Just Buy Chargers<br />Off a Shelf.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/55 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Fleet depots have unique electrical constraints, operational rhythms, and uptime requirements that off-the-shelf charging products aren't designed for. Getting it wrong means stranded vehicles, angry drivers, and a budget hole.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/8 p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Electrical Capacity Limits</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Most depot sites weren't built for simultaneous high-draw charging. Without load management and infrastructure upgrades, you'll trip breakers before you charge half your fleet.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/8 p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Shift Scheduling Complexity</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Multi-shift operations need vehicles charged at specific windows — not whenever a charger happens to be free. Smart scheduling and prioritization must be built into the system from day one.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/8 p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Depot Layout & Cable Run</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Physical placement of chargers affects usability, throughput, and cost. Poor depot design leads to cable hazards, congested lanes, and wasted infrastructure spend.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/8 p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Grid Demand Charges</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Unmanaged charging creates peak demand spikes that show up as punishing demand charges on your utility bill. Open ADR 2.0b integration and smart load spreading eliminate this risk.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/8 p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Maintenance & Uptime Risk</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            A broken charger at a public station is an inconvenience. At a fleet depot, it's a vehicle that doesn't leave the yard. Proactive maintenance and remote diagnostics aren't optional — they're table stakes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/8 p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Capital & Budget Pressure</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Upfront infrastructure investment competes with vehicle acquisition, facility costs, and operations budgets. Available financial models — including no-cost and leasing — let you electrify without a capital commitment.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       WHAT EVIUM DESIGNS FOR FLEETS
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-[#0d1f2b] py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">

        <div>
          <p class="text-evium-green text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-4">Engineered for Your Operation</p>
          <h2 class="text-white font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-6">
            A Charging Strategy.<br />Not Just Hardware.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/55 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
            Evium starts with your fleet — its size, vehicle types, shift patterns, and depot layout — and works backward to design an infrastructure solution that fits. Every depot is different. Every solution we deliver is built for that depot.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-6">

            <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-evium-green/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">Depot Site Assessment & Layout Design</h4>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Full electrical survey, cable run planning, charger placement, and capacity upgrade roadmap before a single shovel hits the ground.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-evium-green/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">Smart Load Management (Open ADR 2.0b)</h4>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Dynamic load balancing distributes available power across all active chargers, avoiding demand spikes while ensuring every vehicle charges on schedule.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-evium-green/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">Mixed L2 + DCFC Configurations</h4>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Overnight depot charging with Level 2 for standard dwell times, DC fast charging for vehicles that need a quick turn between runs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-evium-green/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">Phased Rollout Capability</h4>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Start with a pilot group of vehicles and scale incrementally as your fleet electrifies — no need to build the full depot on day one.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-evium-green/15 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-base mb-1">Permit, Utility & Compliance Management</h4>
                <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Evium handles every permit, utility interconnection application, and regulatory requirement — so your team doesn't have to become EV infrastructure experts.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: image + accent -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-evium-green/5 blur-3xl rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
          <img
            src="/images/chargers/tellus/evium-dc-fast-outdoor-kiosk-combo.png"
            alt="Evium DC Fast Charging Outdoor Kiosk"
            class="relative w-full max-w-md mx-auto object-contain drop-shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(45,200,86,0.18)]"
          />
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HARDWARE FOR FLEET DEPOTS
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">

      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <p class="text-evium-green text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-4">Proven Fleet Hardware</p>
        <h2 class="text-white font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-6">
          The Right Charger<br />for Every Role.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/55 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Fleet depots typically require a mix of charging speeds. Evium sources, installs, and integrates hardware from GSA-approved manufacturers — including Siemens eMobility partners — built for commercial duty cycles.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <!-- L2 Card -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/8 p-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start group hover:border-evium-green/30 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <img
              src="/images/chargers/evocharge/evium-evocharge-l2-wallmount.png"
              alt="Level 2 Wall-Mount Charger"
              class="w-28 h-40 object-contain drop-shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(45,200,86,0.15)]"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="inline-block text-evium-green text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.2em] uppercase bg-evium-green/10 px-3 py-1 mb-4">Level 2 · Overnight Depot</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-black text-2xl mb-3">L2 Wall-Mount & Pedestal</h3>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">
              Ideal for vehicles with standard dwell times — last vehicle in at night, first vehicle out in the morning. 7.2–19.2 kW output charges most light-duty and medium-duty EVs overnight. Lowest infrastructure cost per port.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/50 text-sm">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></span>
                7.2 kW – 19.2 kW output
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/50 text-sm">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></span>
                OCPP 1.6+ compatible
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/50 text-sm">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Integrated load management
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/50 text-sm">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Best for: vans, passenger EVs, light trucks
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- DCFC Card -->
        <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/8 p-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start group hover:border-evium-green/30 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <img
              src="/images/chargers/maxicharger/maxicharger-dc-fast-60-240kw.png"
              alt="MaxiCharger DC Fast Charger 60-240kW"
              class="w-28 h-40 object-contain drop-shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(45,200,86,0.15)]"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="inline-block text-evium-green text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.2em] uppercase bg-evium-green/10 px-3 py-1 mb-4">DC Fast · Quick-Turn</div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-black text-2xl mb-3">MaxiCharger DC Fast 60–240kW</h3>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">
              For vehicles that return mid-shift or need range replenishment before a second run. 60–240 kW DC fast charging adds meaningful range in 20–45 minutes. Critical for transit, delivery, and emergency fleets.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/50 text-sm">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></span>
                60 kW – 240 kW configurable output
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/50 text-sm">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></span>
                CCS / CHAdeMO / NACS compatible
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/50 text-sm">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Remote diagnostics, OTA firmware
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/50 text-sm">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Best for: transit, logistics, emergency services
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Siemens badge -->
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-4 p-6 border border-white/8 bg-evium-dark-light max-w-lg">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-white/55 text-sm">
          <span class="text-white font-semibold">Siemens eMobility Partner.</span> All hardware sourced through GSA-approved manufacturers, ensuring federal program eligibility and commercial-grade reliability.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       SOFTWARE & MONITORING
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-[#0d1f2b] py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">

        <!-- Left: terminal-style UI mock -->
        <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="bg-[#0a1520] border border-evium-green/20 rounded-sm overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Window bar -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 border-b border-white/8 bg-[#0c1b28]">
              <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-white/15"></div>
              <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-white/15"></div>
              <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-white/15"></div>
              <span class="text-white/30 text-xs ml-2 font-mono">Evium Fleet Portal — Live Status</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Mock data rows -->
            <div class="p-6 space-y-3 font-mono text-xs">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-white/5">
                <span class="text-white/40">PORT</span>
